tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_machine_learning_project (
    project_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name TEXT NOT NULL,
    project_description TEXT,
    progress_log JSONB,
    collaboration_notes TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_machine_learning_projects (
 project_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 project_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
 project_description TEXT,
 start_date DATE,
 completion_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_projects (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name TEXT NOT NULL,
    project_description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE progress_logs(
    log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id UUID,
    log_description TEXT,
    log_date TIMESTAMP,
    log_author TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE projects(
    project_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name TEXT,
    project_description TEXT,
    project_start_date DATE,
    project_last_updated TIMESTAMP,
    project_status TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE collaborators(
    collaborator_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    collaborator_name TEXT,
    collaborator_email TEXT,
    collaborator_role TEXT,
    project_id UUID
);

CREATE TABLE documents(
    document_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id UUID,
    document_title TEXT,
    document_content TEXT,
    document_created_at TIMESTAMPTZ,
    document_last_updated TIMESTAMPTZ
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_projects (
  project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  start_date DATE NOT NULL,
  end_date DATE,
  lead_researcher VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE project_documents (
  document_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id INT NOT NULL,
  document_title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  document_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  document_date DATE NOT NULL,
  document_content TEXT
);
